com.sun.jna.platform.win32

Interface Wtsapi32.WTS_INFO_CLASS

  • Enclosing interface:
    Wtsapi32

    public static interface Wtsapi32.WTS_INFO_CLASS
    Contains values that indicate the type of session information to retrieve in a call to the Wtsapi32.WTSQuerySessionInformation(com.sun.jna.platform.win32.WinNT.HANDLE, int, int, com.sun.jna.ptr.PointerByReference, com.sun.jna.ptr.IntByReference) function.
